<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= lang %>">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - <%= t.siteName %></title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    
    <main class="main-content">
        <section class="page-header">
            <div class="container">
                <h1><%= t.contactTitle %></h1>
                <p><%= t.contactSubtitle %></p>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="contact-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="contact-container">
                    <!-- Contact Information -->
                    <div class="contact-info">
                        <h3>Get in Touch</h3>
                        <p>Ready to experience the difference? Contact us today for a free consultation and personalized quote.</p>
                        
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Address</h4>
                                <p><%= t.footer.address %></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Phone</h4>
                                <p><%= t.footer.phone %></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Email</h4>
                                <p><%= t.footer.email %></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Business Hours</h4>
                                <p>Monday - Friday: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM<br>
                                Saturday: 9:00 AM - 4:00 PM<br>
                                Sunday: Closed</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="social-section">
                            <h4>Follow Us</h4>
                            <div class="social-links">
                                <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                                <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                                <a href="#" aria-label="Twitter"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                                <a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Contact Form -->
                    <div class="contact-form">
                        <h3>Send Us a Message</h3>
                        <form id="contact-form">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="name"><%= t.name %> *</label>
                                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="email"><%= t.email %> *</label>
                                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="phone"><%= t.phone %></label>
                                <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone">
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="services"><%= t.selectServices %></label>
                                <div class="services-selection">
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="refrigerator">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.refrigerator %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="windows">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.windows %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="toilet">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.toilet %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="bathroom">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.bathroom %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="mirrors">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.mirrors %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="floor">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.floor %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="windowsills">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.windowsills %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="carpetStains">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.carpetStains %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="wallStains">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.wallStains %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="oven">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.oven %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="cabinets">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.cabinets %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="service-option">
                                        <label>
                                            <input type="checkbox" name="services" value="dusting">
                                            <%= t.serviceList.dusting %>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="message"><%= t.message %> *</label>
                                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required placeholder="Tell us about your cleaning needs, preferred date/time, and any special requirements..."></textarea>
                            </div>
                            
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                                <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i>
                                <%= t.sendMessage %>
                            </button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- FAQ Section -->
        <section class="faq-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <div class="faq-grid">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>How do I get a quote?</h4>
                        <p>Simply fill out our contact form or call us directly. We'll provide a free, no-obligation quote based on your specific needs.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>Are you insured and bonded?</h4>
                        <p>Yes, we are fully insured and bonded for your peace of mind. All our staff are background-checked and trained professionals.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>What cleaning products do you use?</h4>
                        <p>We use eco-friendly, non-toxic cleaning products that are safe for your family and pets while being effective against dirt and germs.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>Do I need to be home during cleaning?</h4>
                        <p>No, you don't need to be home. Many of our clients prefer to have their space cleaned while they're at work or running errands.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>How long does a typical cleaning take?</h4>
                        <p>Cleaning time varies based on the size of your space and services selected. Most standard cleanings take 2-4 hours.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h4>What if I'm not satisfied?</h4>
                        <p>We guarantee your satisfaction. If you're not happy with our service, we'll return within 24 hours to make it right at no extra charge.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/contact.js"></script>
</body>
</html>